MatchedRegion.transcript: First, we verify that most concepts had little effects on the output, which verifies the sparsity of encoded concepts.
This is a distinctive property of symbolism, where it is sufficient to use a small number of salient symbolic concepts to represent the knowledge.
Such a concept emergent phenomenon has also been mathematically proved in our recent work.

MatchedRegion.Text: Actually, in our recent work [Ren et al., 2023] , we have mathematically proved the above sparse concept emerging phenomenon.
